{
  "page": "Tourney at Lannisport",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For For the tourney in Lannisport before Robert's Rebellion, see <a href=\"/index.php/Tournament_in_honor_of_Viserys%27s_birth\" title=\"Tournament in honor of Viserys&#39;s birth\">tournament in honor of Viserys's birth</a>.</div>\n<p>The <b>tourney at Lannisport</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Tourney\" title=\"Tourney\">tourney</a> held outside of <a href=\"/index.php/Lannisport\" title=\"Lannisport\">Lannisport</a> to celebrate King <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_I_Baratheon\" title=\"Robert I Baratheon\">Robert I Baratheon</a>'s victory over <a href=\"/index.php/Greyjoy%27s_Rebellion\" title=\"Greyjoy&#39;s Rebellion\">Greyjoy's Rebellion</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/289_AC\" title=\"289 AC\">289&#160;AC</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#The_Joust\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">The Joust</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Final\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Final</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Attendees\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Attendees</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tourney_at_Lannisport&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The victor of the joust was Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Jorah_Mormont\" title=\"Jorah Mormont\">Jorah Mormont</a>, who wore the favor of <a href=\"/index.php/Lynesse_Hightower\" title=\"Lynesse Hightower\">Lynesse Hightower</a> and was awarded the win by King <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_I_Baratheon\" title=\"Robert I Baratheon\">Robert I Baratheon</a> after breaking nine lances against Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a>. Jorah crowned Lynesse his <a href=\"/index.php/Queen_of_love_and_beauty\" title=\"Queen of love and beauty\">queen of love and beauty</a>, requesting and receiving her hand in marriage from her father, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Leyton_Hightower\" title=\"Leyton Hightower\">Leyton Hightower</a>, that night. The pair then wed in <a href=\"/index.php/Lannisport\" title=\"Lannisport\">Lannisport</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok12.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok12.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Joust\">The Joust</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tourney_at_Lannisport&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The Joust\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Mormont\" title=\"House Mormont\"><img alt=\"House Mormont.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/46/House_Mormont.svg/32px-House_Mormont.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/46/House_Mormont.svg/48px-House_Mormont.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/46/House_Mormont.svg/64px-House_Mormont.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Mallister\" title=\"House Mallister\"><img alt=\"House Mallister.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/75/House_Mallister.svg/32px-House_Mallister.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/75/House_Mallister.svg/48px-House_Mallister.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/75/House_Mallister.svg/64px-House_Mallister.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Jorah_Mormont\" title=\"Jorah Mormont\">Jorah Mormont</a> defeated Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Jason_Mallister\" title=\"Jason Mallister\">Jason Mallister</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok12.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok12.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Mormont\" title=\"House Mormont\"><img alt=\"House Mormont.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/46/House_Mormont.svg/32px-House_Mormont.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/46/House_Mormont.svg/48px-House_Mormont.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/46/House_Mormont.svg/64px-House_Mormont.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Royce\" title=\"House Royce\"><img alt=\"House Royce.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/cf/House_Royce.svg/32px-House_Royce.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/cf/House_Royce.svg/48px-House_Royce.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/cf/House_Royce.svg/64px-House_Royce.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Jorah_Mormont\" title=\"Jorah Mormont\">Jorah Mormont</a> defeated Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Yohn_Royce\" title=\"Yohn Royce\">Yohn Royce</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok12.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok12.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Mormont\" title=\"House Mormont\"><img alt=\"House Mor